Hayley Adams, 29, of Barnstaple, Devon, was seen sneaking into William Tanner’s bedroom and taking cash from his coat .
Her daughter Angela Wrenn, 56, was shocked to discover the culprit was a trusted relative - and the mother of Mr Tanner's great-grandchildren .
Adams admitted three counts of theft - although she escaped with a community order, restraining order and a total fine of £175 .